Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.19,0:03:35.53,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,He showed up rather early.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.56,0:03:37.93,Mori Shinichi Endo,,0,0,0,,{\blur6.818}Mayai comin'?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.93,0:03:39.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome, of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.93,0:03:41.90,Yamasaki,,0,0,0,,What did he say?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.90,0:03:44.04,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,I couldn't quite catch that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.04,0:03:46.40,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,He's putting too much force on his face.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.61,0:03:48.64,Yamasaki,,0,0,0,,{\c&H000000&\4c&H20DA27&}He can't pronounce things correctly.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.93,0:03:50.83,Mori Shinichi Endo,,0,0,0,,{\blur6.818}I don't need anything right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.83,0:03:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,As you wish. Hey, mister.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.50,0:03:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't look like you're from these parts. Are you a traveler?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.30,0:04:01.52,Mori Shinichi Endo,,0,0,0,,{\blur6.818}Yes, I'm in the middle of a journey,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.53,0:04:04.03,Mori Shinichi Endo,,0,0,0,,{\blur6.818}for a number of reasons.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.63,0:04:05.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.86,0:04:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,In order to repent for your sins, you left your beloved daughter behind and decided to travel alone...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.16,0:04:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,or something like that, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.90,0:04:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,What? You're gonna ignore me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.40,0:04:19.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Somebody!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.70,0:04:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Somebody help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.03,0:04:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, young lady?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.60,0:04:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.73,0:04:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.00,0:04:30.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew you'd come here!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.66,0:04:31.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Get over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.63,0:04:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey miss, we're really bored.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.50,0:04:36.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Come play with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.23,0:04:38.23,Default,,0,0,0,,No, please stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.23,0:04:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.36,0:04:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop that right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.66,0:04:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.20,0:04:44.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, guys! Let's get her out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.63,0:04:48.33,Mori Shinichi Endo,,0,0,0,,{\blur6.818}Sdop!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.53,0:04:49.67,Hamada,,0,0,0,,{\pos(720,861.818)}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.13,0:04:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Shin-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.40,0:04:54.81,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,It's hard to make out what he says.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.76,0:04:59.24,Mori Shinichi Endo,,0,0,0,,{\blur6.818}Can't you see this young lady doesn't like you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.43,0:05:01.23,Mori Shinichi Endo,,0,0,0,,{\blur6.818}Please let go of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.23,0:05:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know where you came from but,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.30,0:05:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,if you don't want to get hurt, shut-
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.73,0:05:10.23,Hamada,,0,0,0,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.13,0:05:13.96,Mori Shinichi Endo,,0,0,0,,{\blur6.818}I didn't want to get involved but,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.96,0:05:15.96,Mori Shinichi Endo,,0,0,0,,{\blur6.818}pretending to be just a bystander...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.96,0:05:19.06,Mori Shinichi Endo,,0,0,0,,{\blur6.818}will stray a person from the path of righteousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.20,0:05:23.63,Hamada,,0,0,0,,He missed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.96,0:05:28.46,Mori Shinichi Endo,,0,0,0,,{\blur6.818}Hurry up and
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.46,0:05:29.73,Mori Shinichi Endo,,0,0,0,,{\blur6.818}get lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.73,0:05:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't get ahead of yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.40,0:05:33.51,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.51,0:05:35.25,Yamasaki,,0,0,0,,Everyone knows, {\alpha&HFF&}the timing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.25,0:05:36.65,Yamasaki,,0,0,0,,Everyone knows, the timing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.66,0:05:41.16,Yamasaki,,0,0,0,,Here they come.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.23,0:05:46.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Kill him!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.33,0:05:46.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
