Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.40,0:05:56.20,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,His face stopped looking like {\alpha&HFF&}Mori Shinichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.20,0:05:58.00,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,His face stopped looking like {\c&H000000&\4c&H0D2ACB&}Mori Shinichi{\c&H0D2ACB&\4c&H000000&}.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.97,0:06:03.41,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Wait, {\alpha&HFF&}he didn't hit him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.41,0:06:05.41,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Wait, he didn't hit him.
