Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.80,0:06:30.47,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,He's way too strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.01,0:06:41.75,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,{\pos(721.6,901.091)}There's no {\alpha&HFF&}feeling of danger {\c&H0D2ACB&\4c&H000000&}at all.
