Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.90,0:06:44.45,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,I agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.73,0:06:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Could it be? Father?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.95,0:06:50.12,Yamasaki,,0,0,0,,{\pos(721.6,861.818)}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.12,0:06:53.56,Hamada,,0,0,0,,{\pos(718.4,898.909)}That kind of twist?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.20,0:06:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,,That sword looks exactly like the one my father used.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.70,0:06:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It's you, isn't it, father?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.60,0:06:58.16,Mori Shinichi Endo,,0,0,0,,{\blur6.818}I do not...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.16,0:07:00.16,Mori Shinichi Endo,,0,0,0,,{\blur6.818}have a daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.16,0:07:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you saying!? Didn't you say you left your daughter behind to go on a journey!?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.33,0:07:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Father, it's me, Koyuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.76,0:07:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I went on a journey to find you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.46,0:07:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Father...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.73,0:07:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's live together again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.80,0:07:17.40,Mori Shinichi Endo,,0,0,0,,{\blur6.818}Koyuki-san, I will...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.40,0:07:20.83,Mori Shinichi Endo,,0,0,0,,{\blur6.818}continue my journey until I repent my sins.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.63,0:07:28.93,Mori Shinichi Endo,,0,0,0,,{\blur6.818}However, if she found it in herself to forgive me one day, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.26,0:07:32.33,Mori Shinichi Endo,,0,0,0,,{\blur6.818}I want my live together...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.00,0:07:34.60,Hamada,,0,0,0,,{\pos(720,905.455)}They're taking a lot of {\c&H000000&\4c&HE60C1D&}pictures{\c&HFF0000&}.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.60,0:07:35.26,Mori Shinichi Endo,,0,0,0,,{\blur6.818}with my daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.34,0:07:40.47,Yamasaki,,0,0,0,,It's that kind of moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.47,0:07:43.17,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,{\pos(721.6,907.636)} I guess it's fine to take pictures.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.20,0:07:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Traveler...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.20,0:07:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you at least tell me where you're heading?
